---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-950 border-t border-white/10 mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-2xl">🧖</span>
        <span class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-wider">SAUNA LOG</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm text-center max-w-md">
        全国のサウナ施設を巡り、本音のレビューをお届けするサウナブログ。
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-4">
        &copy; {year} tsuyoshishirota.com All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
